        "content": "\ud83c\udfad Welcome to the Formal Debate!\n\n\ud83d\udccb **Topic**: The Impact of Social Media on Society\n\n\ud83d\udc65 **Participants and Positions**:\n  \u2022 TechOptimist: Social media is a net positive\n  \u2022 DigitalWellbeing: Social media needs mental health reforms\n  \u2022 PrivacyAdvocate: Social media violates privacy rights\n\n\ud83d\udcdc **Debate Format** (traditional):\n1. Main Arguments - Each participant makes 1 arguments\n2. Rebuttals - Participants respond to opposing arguments\n\n\u2696\ufe0f **Rules**:\n  \u2022 Participants must argue for their assigned position\n\nLet us begin! TechOptimist, please present your opening statement.",
